                            <comment id="13470564" author="gtully" created="Fri, 5 Oct 2012 19:02:30 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;a workaround is to avoid page overflow by configuring a large index page size for kahadb. The size needs to be &amp;gt; any single stored value. In the case of offline durables with selectors the sequence set of pending messages needs to fit in one page.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
